msgid "Enable/disable thread archiving for this board (not available if load balancer is used). If enabled, when a thread is pruned or deleted through this panel with the archive checkbox checked, the thread and its images will be moved into the arch directory, found in the same directory as the board. To function properly, you must create and set proper permissions to /boardname/arch, /boardname/arch/res, /boardname/arch/src, and /boardname/arch/thumb"
